{
  "texts": [
    "The following sections explain each component of the NLP pipeline.",
    "We collected mainstream media data from Nexis foot_0 which offers access to a vast database of media sources.",
    "A manual analysis of articles retrieved using the search query \"energy crisis\" revealed that crisis talk was initiated during the period of early 2014 and gradually evolved into a central topic in the early 2020s.",
    "From the initial data collection we extracted further closely associated keywords that still referred to the main aspect of our study, i.e.",
    "the cost of energy and the impact of this cost."
  ]
}